Next.js Application

## Project

- Next.js TypeScript application using App Router.
- Component development with React.
- Use Tailwind CSS for styling design.
- Use Shadcn UI components.
- Use React Context for state management.
- Use next-intl for internationalization.

## Rules

- Implement type safety using TypeScript.
- Follow React best practices and hooks.
- Achieve responsive design using Tailwind CSS and Shadcn UI.
- Maintain a consistent internationalization structure.
- Maintain the modularity and reusability of components.
- Use correct type definitions for components and data.